        "type": "synthdef",
        "source": "// Genre: Pop, R&B | Character: Breathy vocal texture\ndefine_synthdef(\"vocal_breathy\")\n    .param(\"freq\", 220.0)\n    .param(\"amp\", 0.5)\n    .param(\"gate\", 1.0)\n    .body(|freq, amp, gate| {\n        let envelope = env_asr(0.15, 1.0, 0.25);\n        let env = NewEnvGenBuilder(envelope, gate)\n            .with_done_action(2.0)\n            .build();\n\n        // Soft vibrato\n        let vib = sin_osc_ar(4.5) * freq * 0.005;\n\n        // Pitched component\n        let pitched = saw_ar(freq + vib) * 0.25;\n\n        // Breath noise\n        let breath = bpf_ar(pink_noise_ar(), freq * 2.0, 0.3) * 0.35;\n\n        // Formants\n        let mix = pitched + breath;\n        let f1 = bpf_ar(mix, 600.0, 0.12) * 0.4;\n        let f2 = bpf_ar(mix, 1200.0, 0.15) * 0.3;\n\n        let sig = f1 + f2;\n\n        sig * env * amp\n    });\n",
